    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Writing It Down]]></title>
    <link href="http://arriolac.github.io/blog/2012/02/25/writing-it-down/"/>
    <updated>2012-02-25T00:00:00-08:00</updated>
    <id>http://arriolac.github.io/blog/2012/02/25/writing-it-down</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><strong>"Most slow hunches never last long enough to turn into something useful, because they pass in and out of our memory too quickly, precisely because they possess a certain murkiness. You get a feeling that there's an interesting avenue to explore, a problem that might someday lead you to a solution, but then you get distracted by more pressing matters and the hunch disappears. So part of the secret of hunch cultivation is simple: write everything down." </strong>
<p style="text-align:right;"><strong></strong><em>—</em> <em>Steven Johnson</em></p>
</blockquote>

]]></content>
